description: minimalist productivity launcher Aster Launcher - the minimalist productivity launcher for focus, productivity, keep your focus on what really counts. Feature Favorite App Quick Access: Display your favorite apps in text format on the home screen for swift access to your most-used apps, streamlining your operations. Hide Apps: Easily conceal apps that you don't want to be visible, keeping your home screen clean and focused on the content you need. App Locking: Secure your privacy and data by setting passwords to lock selected apps. Personalized Customization: Choose the font color and position for time, date, and favorite apps, making your home screen truly reflect your style.
